726522f-b.text:
Eldert Street (left), south from Wyckoff Ave. to Long Island Railroad right of way, in a set of two views. No.1 shows the S.W. and No. 2 the S.E. corners. View No. 1 is in Brooklyn and View No. 2 shows the dividing line which is the center of the Street;
and a line of garages on the Queens County side.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
